  "contentHtml": "<img src=\"https://mcusercontent.com/be20bbfba341582993786f7f0/images/6e143325-c7c7-37f3-3355-975fc53161bb.png\" width=\"628\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<p><span>Hey Brew Shop Fam!<br>Here's an update of what's happening this week - from new&nbsp;beer drops, wine reviews, our current tap list, to upcoming tastings, and more.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<img src=\"https://mcusercontent.com/be20bbfba341582993786f7f0/images/9bb2d0a6-3492-ed09-d710-628f409a836c.png\" width=\"520\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<p><span><span>We're excited to bring back </span></span><strong><span><span>The Brew Shop 6 Roses of Spring</span></span></strong><span>! Nothing hails the beginning of warm weather quite like Rose and we're here to help you ring it in with 6 fresh Roses. Available in limited quantities by pre-order, make sure you grab yours before they sell out!</span></p>\n<p><span><span><span>Our 6 Roses of Spring will be hand-selected by your favorite winos (Beth, Julie &amp; Aidan) and filled with never-before-seen-in-the-shop Rose. What's included is a surprise, but each pack will contain ONE sparkler and FIVE still Roses.</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span>6 Roses of Spring packs will be available for pick-up beginning </span></span></span><strong><span><span><span>Thursday, May 7th</span></span></span></strong><span><span> - just in time for </span></span><strong><span><span><span>Mother's Day</span></span></span></strong><span><span>, if that special Mom in your life adores Rose!</span></span><em><span><span><span>Wine Club Member? Remember to put in your special code at check out for 10% off!</span></span></span></em></p>\n<img src=\"https://mcusercontent.com/be20bbfba341582993786f7f0/images/0637feeb-75f2-c835-7e0f-fe1f83576fb0.jpeg\" width=\"565\" alt=\"BlackandBlueSummerPhotoLifeQuoteInstagramPostInstagramPost45_1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<p>Plan ahead Arlington! We’ll be closed this Sunday for a staff outing. Normal hours Saturday so hit us up then!</p>\n<img src=\"https://mcusercontent.com/be20bbfba341582993786f7f0/images/21996ce7-309a-732a-500d-57b4987ce753.png\" width=\"520\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<p>Join us this<strong> Friday from 5-7 PM</strong> as we welcome<strong> Brothers Brewing </strong>for our free tasting! Scroll down to see our full tasting lineup for April!</p>\n<img src=\"https://mcusercontent.com/be20bbfba341582993786f7f0/images/ee115cd0-d500-a2d3-3838-9a17f000daf8.jpeg\" width=\"298\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<p><span><span><span><span>🌾 Fresh </span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span>Wheatland Spring</span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span> restock!<br>• </span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span>Return Estate</span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span> Pilsner<br>• </span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span>Koln Calling</span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span> Kolsch<br>• </span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span>Farm Chores</span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span> Golden Ale<br>•</span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span> Dusk</span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span> Hazy IPA<br>•</span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span> Wildflower Lager</span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span> conditioned on wild yeast</span></span></span></span></p>\n<img src=\"https://mcusercontent.com/be20bbfba341582993786f7f0/images/4f9bd023-bd2e-fe8c-6d95-b2b8477a6bc9.jpeg\" width=\"298\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<p><span><span><span><span>🍜 Hello,</span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span> Clag</span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span>!<br>•</span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span> Pool Steak</span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span> Hazy DIPA with Mosaic, Nelson &amp; Simcoe<br>• </span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span>Absolutely Nothing </span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span>Hazy IPA with Simcoe, Nelson Sauvin &amp; Rakau<br>• </span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span>Roadrunner</span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span> Hazy DIPA with Strata &amp; Riwaka</span></span></span></span></p>\n<img src=\"https://mcusercontent.com/be20bbfba341582993786f7f0/images/b14f8c3c-60fe-b82c-9359-6dace57caaa4.jpeg\" width=\"298\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<p><span><span><span><span>🗞️ </span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span>Weldwerks</span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span> returns with all the juice<br>• </span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span>Juicy Bits</span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span> Hazy IPA with Citra, Mosaic &amp; El Dorado<br>• </span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span>Extra Extra Juicy Bits</span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span> DDH Hazy IPA with Citra, Mosaic &amp; El Dorado<br>• </span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span>Hop Creature</span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span> Hazy DIPA<br></span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span>• Haze Drop Sultana Krush </span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span>Hazy IPA with Krush,</span></span></span></span><strong></strong><span><span><span><span>El Dorado &amp; Sultana<br>•</span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span> Twisting Bines</span></span></span></span></strong><span><span><span><span> West Coast IPA with Terpenes and Cascade, Chinook, Citra, Helios &amp; Simcoe</span></span></span></span></p>\n<img src=\"https://mcusercontent.com/be20bbfba341582993786f7f0/images/f335bd68-ac7b-7c49-c5ea-0748a77e6e9d.jpeg\" width=\"298\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<p><s